# About
This script is used to notify the status of a determined package.  
The script goes to a website(correios), specifically, the tracking section, insert the tracking code,and click on the submit button.  
On the next page, the script select two pieces of information, the update date, and the package status, notifying the user.  
  
The script was written and tested on Linux Mint 20 using Python3, Selenium e Notify-send.  
It's possible to utilize CronJobs to schedule the execution of the script.  
